name: The Beginning of the End
description: Jennelle can't stop arguing with Kieffer and roommate Tori. Adam breaks up with Chelsea the same day she is supposed to start a new job. Leah is furious when Corey decides not to move after all and tells her he'd rather buy a truck. Leah wants something better for their girls to live in. Jo refuses to pay the court-mandated child support granted Kailyn.
